{"article_id":"bpDsGSVXtsyO6lka","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"CHARLESTON , S.C. -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Dylann Roof , 21 , has been captured in Shelby , North Carolina , after a massive manhunt in connection with the shooting deaths of nine people at a historically black church in Charleston , South Carolina .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"He was apprehended during a traffic stop ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"after police were alerted some type of \" suspicious activity , \"","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"authorities said .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Charleston Police Chief Greg Mullen said","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Roof \" obviously committed a tragic , heinous crime last night in the city of Charleston . \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"He credited \" unparalleled cooperation \" between law enforcement agencies for the quick arrest .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Chief Mullen said","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Roof was taken into custody without incident .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Earlier Thursday , police released photographs of the young , white man","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"suspected of being the gunman","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"who shot and killed nine people at a historic black church during a Wednesday night prayer meeting .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Confederate flag fight :","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Nikki Haley blasted by ex-Obama official in wake of Charleston shooting","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The FBI said","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"it was searching for Dylann Roof , 21 , Thursday morning ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and noted","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"he was 5-foot-9 , and approximately 120 pounds ,","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"and that he he may be driving a black 2000 Hyundai Elantra sedan .","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"Roof has been arrested twice as an adult ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"one a drug-related offense and the other a trespassing charge .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"He was out on bond at the time of the shooting rampage ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"court records show .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"The Justice Department ' s Civil Rights Division , the FBI and the U.S. Attorney ' s Office for the District of South Carolina are opening a hate crime investigation into the shooting .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"The suspect joined the prayer group inside the church for an hour","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"before opening fire at about 9 p.m. Wednesday ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Chief Mullen said .","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"The deadly attack at Emmanuel AME church , one of the oldest black church in the country , shook Charleston","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"and sent shockwaves across the country .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Speaking on the floor of the U.S. House ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"Rep. Jeff Duncan , South Carolina Republican , asked lawmakers to please pray for the 180-year-old Emanuel African Methodist Episcopal Church and those impacted by the shooting .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"\" Tragedy shot through the heart of every family and community last night in South Carolina , \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Duncan said .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"\" It is important at times like these to remember","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that we are all made in the image of God .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"We are all brothers and sisters in Christ","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"and are there","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"to share the burden of tragedy and loss .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"\" We all need to come together with compassion and love , \"","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Republican presidential candidate Jeb Bush canceled a campaign event Thursday morning in Charleston","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"because of the shooting .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , another 2016 GOP presidential candidate , said","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"he was cancelling scheduled campaign stops in Philadelphia and New Hampshire this weekend","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"in order to return home .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"Sen. Tim Scott said on Thursday","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"that he wanted \" swift justice \" for those","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"who were killed during the shooting .","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"The South Carolina Republican made the comments","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"after catching a flight from Washington , D.C. , to his home state Thursday morning .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"\" The horror","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that occurred at Mother Emanuel last night","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"has truly devastated our community , \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Scott said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"\" Emanuel AME means so much to so many ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"and we stand by them today","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"as they mourn the loss of their leader and brothers and sisters in Christ .","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Pastor Pinckney was a good man , an honest man and a wonderful representative for his congregation . \"","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"The Rev . Al Sharpton ,","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"who has been a fixture at scenes of racial unrest ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"he was likely heading to Charleston .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"\" I will do whatever is helpful to the families and the situation , \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Mr. Sharpton told MSNBC ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"where he works as an on-air personality .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Chief Mullen said","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that investigators did not know","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"if the suspect was still in the Charleston area .","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"local , state and federal law enforcement agencies on the East Coast had been alerted","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"to be on the lookout for the suspect .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"\" We ' ve got a good starting point here .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"We ' ve got a good suspect","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"and what we need now is to get the assistance of the community , \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"After the shooting ,","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"groups gathered for prayer vigils outside the church .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Community organizer Christopher Cason said","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"he felt certain","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"the shootings were racially motivated .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"\" I am very tired of people telling me","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"that I don ' t have the right","depth":16},{"id":84,"text":"to be angry , \"","depth":16},{"id":85,"text":"Mr. Cason said .","depth":14},{"id":86,"text":"\" I am very angry right now . \"","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Charleston Mayor Joseph P. Riley called the shooting \" the most unspeakable and heartbreaking tragedy . \"","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"\" The only reason","depth":16},{"id":89,"text":"that someone could walk into a church","depth":17},{"id":90,"text":"and shoot people","depth":18},{"id":91,"text":"praying","depth":18},{"id":92,"text":"is out of hate , \"","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"Mr. Riley said","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"told reporters Wednesday night .","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"\" It is the most dastardly act","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"that one could possibly imagine ,","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"and we will bring that person to justice .","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"... This is one hateful person . \"","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"When police arrived on the chaotic scene Wednesday night ,","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"they found eight people shot dead inside the church .","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"Another victim died later at a nearby hospital ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"police said .","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"State Sen. Clementa Pinckney ,","depth":16},{"id":104,"text":"who served as a pastor at the church ,","depth":16},{"id":105,"text":"was among those killed ,","depth":15},{"id":106,"text":"The Associated Press reported .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"Pinckney 41 , was a married father of two","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"who was elected to the state house at age 23 ,","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"making him the youngest member of the House at the time .","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"The attack came two months after the fatal shooting of an unarmed black man , Walter Scott , by a white police officer in neighboring North Charleston","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"that sparked major protests","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and highlighted racial tensions in the area .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"The officer has been charged with murder ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"and the shooting prompted South Carolina lawmakers to push through a bill","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"helping all police agencies in the state get body cameras .","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"Pinckney was a sponsor of that bill .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"In a statement , Gov . Nikki Haley asked South Carolinians to pray for the victims and their families","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"and decried violence at religious institutions .","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"\" We ' ll never understand what motivates anyone to enter one of our places of worship","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"and take the life of another , \"","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"The police chief urged people to phone in tips to a hot line : 1-800-CALL-FBI .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"\" Regardless of how small people think","depth":15},{"id":124,"text":"that the information","depth":17},{"id":125,"text":"they have","depth":17},{"id":126,"text":"might be ,","depth":16},{"id":127,"text":"we want them to call us , \"","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"\" We have investigative teams","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"that are ready to go out","depth":15},{"id":131,"text":"and follow every lead","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"sent in to this hotline number .","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"And that ' s what we really need at this point . \"","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"tips had already come in from across the county.","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"- This article is based in part on wire service reports .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":273,"left":0,"right":272,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":272,"left":271,"right":136,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":151,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":145,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":140,"right":142,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":140,"left":1,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":138,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":141,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":144,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":150,"left":147,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":10,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":13,"right":148,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":176,"right":269,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":176,"left":165,"right":175,"relation":"elaborat